  </titlealts>
  <body>
  <div>
      <p>
A 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_care_home_without_nursing">Care Home Without Nursing</xref>
 is an 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_organisation_site">ORGANISATION SITE</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
A 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_care_home_without_nursing">Care Home Without Nursing</xref>
 is a 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_care_home">Care Home</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
Examples of 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_care_home_without_nursing">Care Homes Without Nursing</xref>
 include:        </p>
      <ul>
         <li>
            <p>Residential home</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Rest home</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Convalescent home</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Respite care</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Mental health crisis house</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Therapeutic communities.</p>
         </li>
      </ul>
      <p>
For further information on 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_care_home">Care Homes</xref>, see the 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_care_quality_commission">Care Quality Commission</xref>
 website at: 
              <xref href="https://www.cqc.org.uk/what-we-do/services-we-regulate/care-homes"
               scope="external"
               format="html">Care homes</xref>.        </p>
  </div>
